{
  "stem": "9091.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And two years ago when we were in Warsaw, I went to visit.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I didn't have the chance to go in and see it on the inside, but I saw the surroundings.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was a small apartment-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] two rooms, one big room that was the-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the bedroom and the living room and the dining room.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there was another big room, which was the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And my grandmother used to-- there was a bed there too, and the table and chairs.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So my grandmother used to live there, and we used to eat there too.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But since I was only six, I couldn't know that if we are rich or poor.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was enough for me, and I didn't feel any shortage of-- any lack of anything.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Then the war broke out, 1939.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And my father [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] decided before the Germans come in, he'll run away from Warsaw, and he'll go to Russia.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And once he established himself, he finds a place where to stay, he'll bring us over.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "However, it didn't work out according to the plans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And on the way there, he was shot by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And since we didn't hear-- and then the Germans came into Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I remember-- I remember the time before they came in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "There was-- they bombed Warsaw very heavily.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We decided at that time, during the bombardment of Warsaw-- like we lived on the other side of the city of Warsaw, like, which-- which was called Praga, which is kind of the other side of the Vistula, which divided Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So we lived there, and mother's-- my mother's mother lived in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Her name was Leah.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
